-- AUTHui  –  Compact Redesign
-- Changes vs previous:
--   • Element heights reduced: Toggle 22, Slider 40, Button 24, Dropdown/Input/KeyPicker 36, Label 18, Divider 10
--   • Groupbox: 2px left accent bar replaces floating title; title sits in a dedicated 22px header strip
--   • Tab bar: inverted (inactive = filled/dim, active = transparent + accent underline)
--   • Shadows: layer count → 10, max alpha 0.38 → perceptible depth
--   • All interactive elements get a subtle hover tint (accent @ 0.09)
--   • Slider track uses MainColor (visible against BackgroundColor); value label is monospaced-width
--   • Notification slide-in lerp 0.07 → 0.16; tooltip lerp 0.07 → 0.13
--   • Tab switch speed 0.055 → 0.09
--   • Accent-bar language extended: groupbox left edge, active input/keypicker border, notification left pip

